# DataImpulse (and generic) proxy list for FSBO worker rotation.
# One proxy URL per line; used when DATAIMPULSE_PROXY_LIST_PATH points to this file
# (e.g. DATAIMPULSE_PROXY_LIST_PATH=proxies.txt in scripts/redfin-scraper).
# See FSBO_Bulk_Scraper_Pipeline.md §5.1 for env vars and rotation behavior.
#
# Format: with or without "http://" (http:// is added automatically).
# Example (DataImpulse US residential):
# YOUR_LOGIN__cr.us:YOUR_PASSWORD@gw.dataimpulse.com:823
#
# You can paste 2000+ lines (e.g. from DataImpulse). Round-robin uses the next line
# per request. Multiple lines = better distribution; duplicate lines still work.
# Lines starting with # are ignored.
